{"tid":2123253,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"特朗普：中美貿易協議已無實際意義","createTime":"2020-07-24T13:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T14:46:16.000Z","uid":362199,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac8aad46befaf1cf470e78b26b3edade6351572","tid":2123253,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:29:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1030026&amp;newssource=HK6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fmobile%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3DNOW.1030026%26newssource%3DHK6&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=2fa4d005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1030026&amp;newssource=HK6</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，雖然中國最近數周加大採購農產品，但中美貿易協議對他而言意義已不如以往。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，中國購買美國農產品的規模不斷創新高，而昨日是購買粟米量創紀錄，中國購買粟米的數量比以往任何時候都要多，而且持續2至3日；不過與當日簽署貿易協議相比，現時協議對他的意義已大減。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國農業部數據，中國在7月14日購買創紀錄的176萬噸粟米，截至今年7月16日為止中國今年已購買610萬噸大豆。"},{"pid":"ac1f58464c8430d19a99aaff062165397182c69e","tid":2123253,"uid":112748,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4ac8aad46befaf1cf470e78b26b3edade6351572","tid":2123253,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:29:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1030026&amp;newssource=HK6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fmobile%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3DNOW.1030026%26newssource%3DHK6&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=2fa4d005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1030026&amp;newssource=HK6</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，雖然中國最近數周加大採購農產品，但中美貿易協議對他而言意義已不如以往。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，中國購買美國農產品的規模不斷創新高，而昨日是購買粟米量創紀錄，中國購買粟米的數量比以往任何時候都要多，而且持續2至3日；不過與當日簽署貿易協議相比，現時協議對他的意義已大減。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國農業部數據，中國在7月14日購買創紀錄的176萬噸粟米，截至今年7月16日為止中國今年已購買610萬噸大豆。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202